platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Anyone whos booked train tickets in the UK knows it can be a labyrinthine task. Am I buying off-peak tickets? What is off-peak? What is super off-peak? Am I getting the best deal? We were thrilled to have all thisand morefinally made clear as day by a souped-up Trainline app. Its become as essential to our train travel as a fully charged phone battery.
